<body>
<div type="editorialNote">
<head>Bemerkung zur handschriftlichen Vorlage</head>
<p>
                    Das P.S. befindet sich ausschliesslich in der handriftlichen Fassung in UB Basel, L Ia 673:Bl.54. </p>
</div>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1062921" n="6r"/>
<opener>
<lb/><note hand="pers_unknown"><rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place"><choice><abbr>Bas.</abbr><expan>Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></expan></choice></rs> <date when="1710-04-12">12 <choice><abbr>Apr.</abbr><expan>Aprilis</expan></choice> 1710</date></note>
<salute><lb/>Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stantissimo ac Doctissimo Viro 
                    <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D<supplied>.</supplied></abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person"><abbr>Joh.</abbr> Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs></salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Iter Tuum Adgnate Optime quod meditaris in <rs key="place_VER-frankr" type="place">Galliam</rs> ex 
                    <lb/><rs key="brieftag" type="letter">novissimis Tuis</rs> l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus intellexi, illud ut ex animi sententia 
                   <lb/>absolvas, Te<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> nobis Deus reducem reddat salvum et sospi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem, est quod Tibi ardentissime voveo et apprecor.</p>
<p><lb/>Ecce hic <rs key="brieftag" type="letter">litteras</rs> co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endatitias sub sigillo quod ajunt volante
                    <lb/>ad <abbr>Nob.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-103763058" type="person">Fatium</rs>, cui eas postquam lectas obsignaveris
                   <lb/>tradas statim ac <rs key="place_GEO-2660646" type="place">Genev<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> appuleris: Si quid in Tui gratiam
                   <lb/>possit efficere, non dubito quin sit lubens facturus
                    <lb/>pro ea qua est erga me humanitate. Pro hospitio <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Pa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>risiis</rs> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>rendo nondum putem tempus esse, donec con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stiterit certo an et quando illuc sis venturus, quod ubi
                    <lb/>scivero, comitabor Te <rs key="brieftag brieftag" type="letters">litteris</rs><!-- dieser Brief scheint nicht erhalten zu sein, --> ad <abbr>Ill.</abbr> Abbatem <rs key="pers_DE-588-120052539" type="person">Bigno<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nium</rs> et <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119062372" type="person">Varignonium</rs>,<!-- der letzte Brief an Varignon ist vom 17.März 1710 --> qui Tibi ut spero ex co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>en<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>datione mea, ope<del><unclear>sua</unclear></del> et consiliis <add>suis</add> non deerunt. Ad in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>terrogata Tua h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c habe: Quid <abbr>Dn.</abbr> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089640587" type="person">Graffenried</rs> per<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>moverit ut me relicto ad <abbr>Doct.</abbr><!-- evtl. zu Doctissimum expanden --> <rs key="pers_DE-588-129684406" type="person">Platerum</rs> se conferret, haud
                   <lb/>adeo difficile est divinatu, ibi enim libertatem et consortium
                   <lb/>invenit quod neutrum apud me habuit. <rs key="pers_DE-588-1072469103" type="person">Henricum Bec<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>kium</rs> meum quondam co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ensalem resumsisse studia
                    <lb/>juridica, ab ipsius <rs key="pers_DE-588-116073562X" type="person">Patre</rs><!-- Beck Vater --> jam ante audiveram, quod
                   <lb/>ergo bene vortat! Male agis dum refricas mihi me<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>moriam <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089923198" type="person">hominis</rs><note hand="pers_unknown">Verzaglia</note> cujus nomen effari vel scribere horreo,
                   <lb/>loquor de Monstro illo Italico, de Hirco corpore et animo
                   <lb/>olente, qui ex stygia palude ad me missus videtur, partim ut
                <pb facs="1062922" n="6v"/>
<lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>des meas spurcitie et foetore plusquam mephitico adimpleret
                   <lb/>partim etiam et quidem cumprimis ut beneficia mea omnium
                   <lb/>maxima (quid enim fideli informatione majus?) execrabili sce<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lere pro gratiarum actione compensaret, scripta scilicet ad me
                   <lb/>nuper invectiva, qua nihil unquam furiosius excogitari ne<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dum perpetrari potuit: miror <rs key="place_WEI-erdepl" type="place">Terram</rs> hoc monstrum, homi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nis diutius olere velle, vel potius nondum deglutiisse;
                   <lb/>quorsum nunc ipsum abegerint infernales furi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ignoro nec
                    <lb/>anxie anquiro, utinam mihi posthac, nulla<!-- In der Spiesstranskription steht hier [amplius] -->  pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>beatur ansa
                   <lb/>de eo vel cogitandi vel loquendi! Scripsit quidem se <rs key="place_GEW-rheina" type="place">Rheno</rs> se<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cundo <rs key="place_GEO-2925533" type="place">Francofurtum</rs> petiturum, ubi <abbr>Ampl.</abbr> <rs type="person">Leibnitium</rs> sa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lutatum ire se speret, grata <abbr>sc.</abbr> salutatio hircum redolens<unclear>!</unclear>
<lb/>sed absorbebit forte <rs key="place_GEW-rheina" type="place">Rhenus</rs> hoc portentum quod <rs key="place_WEI-erdepl" type="place">Terra</rs>
<lb/>vocare negat, antequam terram attigerit. Senatus nostri
                   <lb/>Academici protestatio contra Rh<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>torum appellationem sinistrum
                   <lb/>habuit successum sicuti omnia qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ab aliquo tempore coram
                   <lb/>Magistratu politico peragenda habuimus, quid mirum! nunc
                   <lb/>ubi tam pauci studiorum Moecenates in illo reperiuntur.
                    <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-117601020" type="person">Montmortio</rs> misi <rs key="biblio_QUAQJMHS" type="biblio">animadversiones</rs><note resp="SG" type="comment">Dieser Brief Joh. I B.s und die Beilage mit den Bemerkungen Nic. I B.s wurden in die zweite Auflage von Montmorts Essay d'Analyse (Paris, 1713) aufgenommen. Montmorts Antwort datiert auf den 15.11.1710.</note> in <rs key="biblio_69NKSR46" type="biblio">libellum suum</rs> et Tuas
                   <lb/>et meas, sed nullam responsionem adhuc <subst><del>de</del><add>ab</add></subst> eo tuli; haud
                   <lb/>dubie de ejusmodi rebus et aliis cum eo agendi et Te in mathe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>maticis exercendi copiosa et frequens dabitur occasio <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Parisiis</rs>.</p>
<closer><lb/>Interim vale ab <rs key="pers_DE-588-108991332X" type="person">uxore</rs> et <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144 pers_DE-588-1153514060 pers_DE-588-118656503 pers_DE-588-1089913494" type="persons">liberis meis</rs> quam plurimum salu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tatus. <dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1710-04-12">XII. Aprilis MDCCX</date>.</dateline></closer>
<postscript><p><abbr>P. S.</abbr><note type="editorial">Das P.S. befindet sich nur in der Fassung UB Basel, L Ia 673:Bl.54.</note> Il y a environ deux mois que je reçus une <rs key="brieftag" type="letter">lettre</rs> de <abbr>Mr.</abbr> <rs key="DE-588)119112450" type="person">Herman</rs> Profe<unclear>s</unclear><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>seur en <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Padoue</rs>, il se porte bien, et s'y plait assez; mais <choice><orig>a</orig><reg>à</reg></choice> ce qu'il me donne <choice><orig>a</orig><reg>à</reg></choice> en<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tendre il souhaiteroit de changer sa station avec une autre en <rs key="place_VER-hollan" type="place">Hollande</rs>,
                    <lb/>quand je luy ecriray je me souviendray de luy dire que vous m'avez <choice><sic>demendé</sic><corr>demandé</corr></choice><del> aprez</del>
<lb/>aprez ses nouvelles. 
                </p></postscript>
</div>
